metadata.name: Totem tree in BXL
metadata.description:
"Looking for fairies" started in Brussels. 
One summer night  I heard a whispering in the park and tried to catch one of their ray of lights. Will you manage to see their shadows ? 
The search is launched in many places now...

PS : Part of the benefits from this sale will be donated to the great sound sharing site Freesound.org.
